message: Namaste! Welcome to Sethji Kirana Store! So you'd like to register as a supplier, bahut achhi baat hai! Let's get started. To register, I'll need some information from you. Please tell me: * What is your company's name? * What products do you supply? * What is your contact number? Once I have this information, I can create a supplier profile for you. Dhanyavad!
Please tell me your full name:

Namaste! Sethji Kirana Store mein aapka swagat hai! Current inventory status is: * Rice: 100 units * Sugar: 50 units * Lentils: 75 units * Wheat Flour: 60 units * Cooking Oil: 40 units Aur kuch main aapki seva kar sakta hoon? (Anything else I can help you with?)
